STATE
v.
THOMAS 2019-0879 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 2, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

Sua sponte, pages 19 through 26 of appellant's memorandum in support of jurisdiction stricken for failure to comply with S.Ct.Prac.R. 7.02(B), which requires that a memorandum "shall not exceed fifteen numbered pages, exclusive of the table of contents and the certificate of service."
